videos.headline: Arizona State opens season with INT
videos.description: Joey Bryant picks off the pass from Tyler Rogers to set up Arizona State.

videos.headline: Arizona State strikes first with Ballage TD
videos.description: Kalen Ballage runs for the corner of the end zone to open up the scoring for Arizona State.

videos.headline: Sun Devils connect on 53 yard TD pass
videos.description: Manny Wilkins finds Jalen Harvey open downfield for the 53 yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Rogers takes it himself for New Mexico State TD
videos.description: New Mexico State quarterback Tyler Rogers fakes the hand off on the play action then dives into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilkins finds receiver deep downfield for 60-yard TD
videos.description: Arizona State quarterback Manny Wilkins lobs the 60-yard pass downfield to John Humphrey for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Ballage's second TD extends Arizona State's lead
videos.description: Kalen Ballage rushes for 20 yards nearly untouched for his second touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Williams returns pick-six 49 yards for ASU
videos.description: Kobe Williams picks off the pass from Tyler Rogers and dodges defenders all the way to the end zone.

videos.headline: Another leaping catch for New Mexico State
videos.description: After review it is confirmed that New Mexico State wide receiver Jaleel Scott came down in-bounds after making another great catch.

videos.headline: New Mexico State scores on 50-yard TD run
videos.description: Jason Huntley dives into the end zone after a 50-yard rush from midfield.

videos.headline: Huntley takes in another New Mexico State TD
videos.description: Tyler Rogers finds Jason Huntley downfield who takes the ball up the sideline for the touchdown.

videos.headline: New Mexico State falls short after last second TD
videos.description: Jaleel Scott makes another amazing catch for a touchdown as time expires, but New Mexico State falls just short against Arizona State 37-31. Scott finishes with eight catches for 149 yards and two scores.
